graph TB
    User([👤 用户])

    subgraph 系统
        WebApp[<b>Web 前端</b><br/><small>React SPA</small>]
        API[<b>API 服务</b><br/><small>FastAPI</small>]
        Worker[<b>异步 Worker</b><br/><small>Celery</small>]
        DB[(<b>数据库</b><br/><small>PostgreSQL</small>)]
        Cache[(<b>缓存</b><br/><small>Redis</small>)]
        MQ[<b>消息队列</b><br/><small>RabbitMQ</small>]
    end

    User -->|HTTPS| WebApp
    WebApp -->|REST API| API
    API -->|SQL| DB
    API -->|读写| Cache
    API -->|发布任务| MQ
    MQ -->|消费任务| Worker
    Worker -->|SQL| DB

    style User fill:#083B77,color:#fff
    style WebApp fill:#4389DB,color:#fff
    style API fill:#4389DB,color:#fff
    style Worker fill:#4389DB,color:#fff
    style DB fill:#7B3DB0,color:#fff
    style Cache fill:#7B3DB0,color:#fff
    style MQ fill:#E08D28,color:#fff
